    {
      "text": "There are four types of stories: Terrestrial, Space, Sengoku, and Gaiden.\nThe storylines in the Terrestrial and Outer Space series are based on the original anime.\nSengoku and Gaiden are scenarios of the warrior Gundam and knight Gundam that were being developed at the time.",
